      <title>小寒抒意</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/10/poem-xiaohan/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/10/poem-xiaohan/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>小寒未落堂前雪，<br>却着暖阳洒西厅。<br>南国风软游人醉，<br>不及北乡霜雪明。</p></blockquote><img src="/2020/06/10/poem-xiaohan/1.jpg" title="小寒">]]></content>
      
      
