      <title>中秋小赋</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/10/poem-middle-festival/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/10/poem-middle-festival/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>浅酌半盏桂花香<br>犹叹初秋夜不凉<br>北国应是风飒飒<br>南境仍未见秋黄</p><p>此间明月白如雪<br>天涯知己在何乡<br>但愿父老身康健<br>此心安处是吾乡</p></blockquote><img src="/2020/06/10/poem-middle-festival/moon1.jpg" title="满月"><img src="/2020/06/10/poem-middle-festival/moon2.jpg" title="满月">]]></content>
      
      
