      <title>异乡与友小聚</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/10/poem-friends/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/10/poem-friends/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>草长莺飞处，<br>蒹葭余落晖。<br>犹忆少年事，<br>情切忘岁催。<br>乡音谈笑足，<br>未曾把酒归。<br>异乡漂泊客，<br>寂寞有人陪。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
