      <title>春雨</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/13/poem-feb-rain/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/13/poem-feb-rain/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>最喜人间二月天，<br>龙神飞过锣鼓喧，<br>天苍地茫雨如瀑，<br>春雷炸醒物万千。</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-feb-rain/1.jpg"><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-feb-rain/2.jpg">]]></content>
      
      
