        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>海桐欲生花，<br>却着满天霞。<br>秋晚露不浓，<br>临树赏灯华。</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-haitong-song/1.jpg"><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-haitong-song/2.jpg">]]></content>
      
      
