        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>秋色未尽雨未歇，<br>冬信渐至霜渐结。<br>江南烟雨慰游子，<br>话罢乡愁拾落叶。</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-home-sick-in-fall/1.jpg"><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-home-sick-in-fall/2.jpg">]]></content>
      
      
