    <entry>
      <title>如梦歌</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>人生如梦似幻，<br>长短不过百年。<br>少壮盛气凌人，<br>老耋涕泪满面。<br>何不得失两忘，<br>带笑风轻云淡。<br>生时和光同尘，<br>弃执弃妄弃慢。<br>死后身归草木，<br>与尔同游轩辕。</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/1.jpg">]]></content>
      
      
